get a lot of support

00:01:24.900 --> 00:01:26.430
on a daily basis.

00:01:26.430 --> 00:01:28.890
I buy a lot of independent
reading books for my students.

00:01:28.890 --> 00:01:31.090
I believe that the smartest
people in the world

00:01:31.090 --> 00:01:32.590
